 Architects 将于明天与乔丹·菲什 (Jordan Fish) 发行新单曲《Curse》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-will-release-new-single-curse-with-jordan-fish-tomorrow-3614997?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=architects-will-release-new-明天与乔丹鱼的单一诅咒Emma WilkesMon, 08 Apr 2024 18:13:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3614997 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="萨姆·卡特和乔丹·菲什" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Fish 于 12 月离开 Bring Me The Horizo​​n，并表示有意成为其他艺术家的词曲作者或制作人</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-will-release-new-single-curse-with-jordan-fish-tomorrow-3614997">Architects 明天将与 Jordan Fish 一起发行新单曲《Curse》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="萨姆·卡特和乔丹·菲什" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/sam-carter-jordan-fish-chiaki-nozu-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/architects">Architects</a>将于明天（4 月 9 日）推出由前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Me The Horizo​​n</a>成员 Jordan Fish 主演的新单曲“Curse”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/architects-the-classic-symptoms-of-a-broken-spirits-album-review-3332859-3332859">建筑师——“破碎精神的经典症状”评论：笨重的连复段和杀手钩子</a></strong></li></ul><p>布莱顿金属乐团在他们的社交媒体上分享了一张带有建筑师“A”标志和歌曲标题的图片来调侃这首歌。照片中标记了 Fish 的 Instagram 账号，表明他参与了他们的新音乐。</p><p> Fish 在他的 Instagram 故事中分享了相同的图片，以及他在工作室里的照片，其中标记了 Architects 主唱 Sam Carter。</p><p>现在，乐队已确认《Curse》将于英国夏令时间明天下午 3 点发行。他们在社交媒体上分享了这首歌的预告片，这似乎表明他们回归了更厚重的根源。</p><p>他们的合作是 Fish 自去年 12 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bring-me-the-horizon-have-parted-ways-with-jordan-fish-3562769">离开 Bring Me The Horizo​​n</a>以来发布的第一首音乐。菲什在一份声明中证实了他在 11 年后离开乐队，表示他将在未来的职业生涯中“暂时专注于歌曲创作和制作”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5YeQsfrRyp/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-